ursuit heads.','Will not do movable jaws, as doing them on foam bases is too difficult. Will not do led''s as I''m not experienced in them enough yet.','PayPal','USD',replace('Most experiences in canines\nwilling to try anything\nWould love to do big cats\nWould love to do fantasy creatures','\n',char(10)));
